# Adapter Parity Rule

Cursor is IDE-primary only when the user chooses it for editing.

Cursor is not governance-primary.

Governance order:

1. Current user instruction
2. `AGENTS.md`
3. `docs/ai/`
4. `docs/skills/`
5. `.cursor/`

Read `docs/ai/adapter-parity.md` if adapter behavior is unclear.
